To run the app (instead of using a manually-installed pyenv on your laptop):
docker-compose run --service-ports app
and then go to localhost:8000/ or localhost:8000/admin

To run the crawl, run this inside the 'app' container:
scrapy crawl fac -a auditee_state=PR -o test.json

